OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. The rest of the night
OL,7,Fwill be mainly dry although rather
OL,8,Fcloudy, perhaps a little rain
OL,9,Fdeveloping across Argyll at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,12,Fspreading to Argyll in the morning,
OL,13,Fthen remaining areas in the afternoon.
OL,14,FA mild morning but becoming somewhat
OL,15,Fcolder in the afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,18,Ffor most of Thursday but rain likely
OL,19,Fby evening. Unsettled with showers or
OL,20,Flonger spells of rain on Friday and
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
